==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Refound
<hw>Re*found"</hw> <pr>(r?*found")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>re-</ets> + <ets>found</ets> to cast; cf. F. <ets>refondare</ets>.
Cf. <er>Refund</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To found or cast
anew.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Ancient bells <xex>refounded</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>T.
Warton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To found or establish again; to
reestablish.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Refound</ent>⟦br⟧

